snippet.title: Slime Rancher Cosplay! DIY
snippet.description:
I have 1 more cosplay for you all for this Halloween season! Today I am going to cosplay as Beatrix from Slime Rancher! I have been loving this game all year so I felt like I had to make a cosplay for this! Leave a LIKE and share if you enjoy!
